<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.4">
<l>vaḷaikkaine ṭuṅkaṇma ṭavā rāycciya rañciya ḻaippa</l>
<l>taḷaittaviḻ tāmaraip poykait taṇtaṭam pukkaṇṭar  kāṇa</l>
<l>muḷaittaye yiṟṟaḻal nākat tucciyil niṉṟatu vāṭa</l>
<l>tilaittamar ceytuva ruvāṉ cittira kūṭattuḷ ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who appeared, entering into the cool pond,</l>
<l rend="indent">a pool with lotus flowers, their tight buds unfurling,</l>
<l>So that the simple herder ladies with bangled arms and long eyes wept, fearing,</l>
<l>Standing on the head of a fiery serpent with fangs shooting [up],</l>
<l rend="indent">as celestials looked on,</l>
<l>Making war, [yet] playing, so that it was defeated,</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one present in Citrakūṭam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
